# Frontend Runtime Role Rules

- Read `docs/ai/services/frontend.md` before large UI changes.
- If the repository family is `web-app`, `pwa`, or `mockup-local`, read the matching family rule together with this rule.
- Preserve existing `ListPage`, `DetailPage`, `RegistrationPage`, `ModifyPage`, `Shared`, `Api` patterns.
- Keep route, type, i18n, and API normalization in sync.
- Prefer existing grid, search-state, and modal patterns.
- Keep project-family assumptions, runtime roles, and command-catalog expectations aligned.
